My second escape map!

ze_wasteland_escape

Spawns: 64
Nuke: Yes
First pic = Spawns
Got a left and a right way from spawns, but both go to the "safe zone".
Theres even a lift that takes you to a safe path.


At the "safe zone" defend it untill the escape arrives, then go inside press the button and ESCAPE.
Then u go down to the underground station and nuke.

Has been tested on Zombie Europe server, by the Css.Eu#CREW
